status.info: We use this protocol and it's working

steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"flssd","text":"After the tissue has been imaged via MALDI IMS, the slide should be placed in a coplin jar or glass petri dish with a solution of room temperature 4% paraformaldehyde in PBS (*must be room temperature).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"r2cf","text":"Discard the PFA (the MALDI IMS matrix will come off the slide in this step).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"a96ir","text":"Add fresh 4% PFA in PBS and shake for 5 more minutes (for a total of 10 minutes in PFA).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ofna","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cvt61","text":" Washing with PFA solution will fix and rehydrate the tissue as the matrix is removed.  This preserves the tissue and antigens, and significantly reduces artifacts.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"39i1t","text":"Add fresh PBS for 3 minutes on shaker. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"alppd","text":"Repeat this wash two more times for a total of 3 times for 3 minutes each.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":17,"length":14}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5qqff","text":" pH should be neutral","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"31nlj","text":"Incubate the slides in 50 mg/mL bovie serum albumin (BSA), 10% (v/v) host-derived serum (depends on which antibodies they use), and 0.5% (v/v) Tween-20 in PBS for 30 minutes.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3bi0b","text":"The tissue should be placed in PBS for 3 minutes on a shaker.  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c2o63","text":"Repeat this wash two more times for a total of 3 times for 3 minutes each.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":17,"length":14}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"40t65","text":"Be very careful. Tissue will be very fragile.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9aa9a","text":"This permeabilizes the tissue slowly. ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"98t87","text":"The Tween cannot be substituted for triton X, as triton X is too harsh and will degrade the tissue. ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cvvj6","text":"30 minutes works for most.  Can do up to 2 hours before the tissue gets very damaged/adherence issues/weird background. ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3oph1","text":"Ensure the donkey serum is reconstituted (10 mL of ddH20)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7560g","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"489v6","text":"2.5 grams of BSA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a8fob","text":"5 mL of reconstituted donkey serum","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4djud","text":"0.25 mL of Tween 20","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cvkpo","text":"44.75 mL of 1X PBS","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9pl4f","text":"---------------------------","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1nrdc","text":"50 mL block solution","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ft3e0","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9a49e","text":"Be very careful.
